{"GYL56hoR7QK":{"id":"GYL56hoR7QK","type":"work","title":"飛鳧語略","authors":[{"name":"沈德符","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《飛鳧語略》•一卷","author_info":"明沈德符撰","summary":"明沈德符撰。德符字虎臣，又字景伯，又字景倩，秀水人。萬曆戊午舉人。此書論字墨法帖及古器真贗之別，皆舉生平所聞見者，凡十八條。其中多與所著《敝帚軒剩語》相同，疑即從《剩語》中抄出者。曹溶《學海類編》乃兩收之，未免失於詳檢也。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/飛鳧語略","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=466430","type":"text"}]},"GYL56h1GkFq":{"id":"GYL56h1GkFq","type":"work","title":"格物粗談","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《格物粗談》•二卷","author_info":"舊本亦題蘇軾撰","summary":"舊本亦題蘇軾撰。分天時、地理等二十門，與世所傳軾《物類相感志》大略相似。後有元範梈識，斷為後人假託。他書亦罕見著錄，惟曹溶收入《學海類編》中。蓋《物類相感志》已出偽作，此更偽書之重佁也。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2}},"GYL56hN2aCf":{"id":"GYL56hN2aCf","type":"work","title":"便民圖纂","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《便民圖纂》•十六卷","author_info":"不著撰人名氏","summary":"不著撰人名氏。第一卷為農務圖十五，第二卷為女紅圖十六，每圖皆系以竹枝詞一首，第三卷以下分十一類，曰耕獲，曰桑蠶，曰樹藝，曰雜占，曰月占，曰祈禳，曰涓吉，曰起居，曰調攝，曰牧養，曰製造。嘉靖壬子刻於貴州。前有左布政使李涵序，稱鄺廷瑞始刻於吳中，呂經又刻於滇省，其中利民用者甚多。然意求全備，往往冗瑣。如末卷載辟鬼魅法，用桃枝灑雄黃水。蓋據《本草》桃枝殺鬼、雄黃殺精魅之說，已為迂闊。又有祛狐狸法，雲妖狸能變形，惟千年枯木能照之，可尋得年久枯木擊之，其形自見。則據張華然華表照斑狸事，衍為此法，殆於兒戲矣。其書本農家者流，然旁及祈福擇日及諸格言，不名一家，故附之雜家類焉。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":16},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=357187","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=7247940","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanliershiyiyuyongqi","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02092573","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆二十一年於永清刻本","version":"v8","total_page":432,"paragraph_count":570,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-jiajingershisanwangz","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056968","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"嘉靖二十三年王貞吉刻藍印本","version":"v5","total_page":413,"paragraph_count":3226,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/YCM294300003","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v3","total_page":362,"paragraph_count":2527,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hveJQF":{"id":"GYL56hveJQF","type":"work","title":"妮古錄","authors":[{"name":"陳繼儒","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《妮古錄》•四卷","author_info":"明陳繼儒撰","summary":"明陳繼儒撰。繼儒有《邵康節外紀》，已著錄。是書多評論字畫古玩，蓋仿趙希鵠《洞天清錄》、周密《雲煙過眼錄》而作，然議論殊為淺陋。","edition":"通行本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4544172","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6427","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v1","total_page":197,"paragraph_count":1527,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlixiushuishenshik","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056989","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆繡水沈氏刻寶顏堂秘笈本","version":"v2","total_page":177,"paragraph_count":1405,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hg9EYw":{"id":"GYL56hg9EYw","type":"work","title":"筠軒清秘錄","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《筠軒清秘錄》•三卷","author_info":"舊本題董其昌撰","summary":"舊本題董其昌撰。其昌有《學科考略》，已著錄。是書凡列目二十有九，皆論玉、石、銅、磁諸古器及法書名畫之類。前有陳繼儒序，謂可與項元汴《薌林清課》並稱。今考其書，即張應文所撰《清秘藏》，但析二卷為三卷。蓋應文之書，近日始有鮑氏知不足齋刊版，附其《子醜真跡日錄》後。從前抄本，流傳不甚顯著。書賈以其昌名重，故偽造繼儒之序以炫俗射利耳。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3}},"GYL56h4kHCT":{"id":"GYL56h4kHCT","type":"work","title":"居家必用事類全集","authors":[],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《居家必用事類全集》•十卷","author_info":"不著撰人名氏","summary":"不著撰人名氏。載歷代名賢格訓及居家日用事宜，以十幹分集，體例頗為簡潔。辛集中有大德五年吳郡徐元瑞《吏學指南序》，聖朝字俱跳行。又《永樂大典》屢引用之，其為元人書無疑。黃虞稷《千頃堂書目》雲，或謂熊宗立撰。恐未必然也。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/居家必用事類全集","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=482245","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=815709","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-longqingerfeilaishan","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02097171","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"隆慶二年飛來山人刻本","version":"v4","total_page":1648,"paragraph_count":13244,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-daikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02038154","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"代刻本","version":"v4","total_page":1668,"paragraph_count":10653,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hyWuG3":{"id":"GYL56hyWuG3","type":"work","title":"岩棲幽事","authors":[{"name":"陳繼儒","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《岩棲幽事》•一卷","author_info":"明陳繼儒撰","summary":"明陳繼儒撰。所載皆山居瑣事，如接花藝木以及於焚香點茶之類，詞意佻纖，不出明季山人之習。自跋稱陳仲子為家於陵，尤可嗤鄙。此沿楊修家子雲之誤也。","edition":"通行本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6428","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":61,"paragraph_count":60,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hBvnLw":{"id":"GYL56hBvnLw","type":"work","title":"都氏鐵網珊瑚","authors":[{"name":"都穆","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《都氏鐵網珊瑚》•二十卷","author_info":"明都穆撰","summary":"明都穆撰。穆有《壬午功臣爵賞錄》，已著錄。是書與世傳朱存理《鐵網珊瑚》同名。（案：存理之書非存理所撰，辨詳本條下，此姑從世俗刊本稱之。）然存理之書分書品、畫品二門，備錄題跋印記，為張醜、郁逢慶諸書所宗，是書則前四卷皆穆所為諸書序跋及書畫題跋，卷五以下即穆所作寓意編。蓋穆嘗以所見書畫別為一書，此又以類相從，附於書目之後。然其中忽雜入《書畫銘心錄》，乃何良俊所撰。第七卷內鶴鵲一條，又忽標《爾雅》二字之目，皆不可解。至第九卷雜錄研銘，皆采自諸家文集，非親見拓本。第十卷以下則鈔偽本張掄《紹興古器評》，十二卷以下則鈔湯垕《四畫鑒》，十五卷後半以下則鈔趙希鵠《洞天清錄》，十八卷以下則鈔周密《雲煙過眼錄》，皆非所自著。蓋奸黠書賈雜裒成編，借穆之名以行也。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":20}},"GYL56hRbUrB":{"id":"GYL56hRbUrB","type":"work","title":"鼂采館清課","authors":[{"name":"費元祿","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《鼂采館清課》•二卷","author_info":"明費元祿撰","summary":"明費元祿撰。元祿字學卿，鉛山人。鉛山之河口有五湖，其一曰官湖，即鼂采湖也。元祿構館其上，因以為名。是書皆記其館中景物及遊賞閒適之事。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5353923","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-mingwanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ89241199902199374945","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"明萬曆刻本","version":"v2","total_page":126,"paragraph_count":276,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056973","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻本","version":"v2","total_page":123,"paragraph_count":161,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hYsMhZ":{"id":"GYL56hYsMhZ","type":"work","title":"考槃餘事","authors":[{"name":"屠隆","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《考槃餘事》•四卷","author_info":"明屠隆撰","summary":"明屠隆撰。隆有《篇海類編》，已著錄。是書雜論文房清玩之事。一卷言書版碑帖，二卷評書畫琴紙，三卷、四卷則筆硯爐瓶，以至一切器用服禦之物皆詳載之，列目頗為瑣碎。其論明一代書家，以祝允明為第一，而文徵明次之。軒輊亦未盡平允。","edition":"通行本"}],"juan_count":{"number":4},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3922785","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishenshishangbai","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY6242","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆沈氏尚白齋刻本","version":"v6","total_page":239,"paragraph_count":156,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY5933","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v6","total_page":228,"paragraph_count":177,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hEr54B":{"id":"GYL56hEr54B","type":"work","title":"水雲錄","authors":[{"name":"楊溥","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《水雲錄》•二卷","author_info":"明楊溥撰","summary":"明楊溥撰。溥，長沙人，自號水雲居士。《千頃堂書目》列於劉基《多能鄙事》後，即以為永樂中石首楊溥。然考書中自述有戎務之暇語，則其人乃嘗為武職者，又所撰有《用藥珍珠囊》，其書成於宏治中。蓋名姓偶同，非一人也。是編上卷載十二月種植花果飲饌及文房雜用。下卷分衛生、養生、器用、牧養四門，所記多農圃種畜法，頗為瑣屑。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2}},"GYL56h8MshR":{"id":"GYL56h8MshR","type":"work","title":"多能鄙事","authors":[{"name":"劉基","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《多能鄙事》•十二卷","author_info":"舊本題明劉基撰","summary":"舊本題明劉基撰。基有《清類天文分野》之書，已著錄。是書凡飲食、器用、方藥、農圃、牧養、陰陽、占卜之法無不備載，頗適於用。然體近瑣碎，若小兒四季關、百日關之類俱見臚列，殊失雅馴。立名取孔子之言，亦屬僣妄。殆託名於基者也。","edition":"浙江汪啟淑家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/多能鄙事","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=8236083","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=619190","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-jiajingsishierfanwei","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02097181","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"嘉靖四十二年範惟一刻本","version":"v5","total_page":526,"paragraph_count":4960,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hJNHrF":{"id":"GYL56hJNHrF","type":"work","title":"李氏居室記","authors":[{"name":"李濂","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《李氏居室記》•五卷","author_info":"明李濂撰","summary":"明李濂撰。濂有《祥符先賢傳》，已著錄。是編乃其退老居鄉，築別墅於郊外。有堂有序，各為撰記。室中器物，悉制箴銘，以寓規警。蓋林居放志之作，故隨所欲言，不以修詞為意雲。","edition":"浙江範懋柱家天一閣藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":5}},"GYL56hjoWuM":{"id":"GYL56hjoWuM","type":"work","title":"墨林快事","authors":[{"name":"安世鳳","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《墨林快事》•十二卷","author_info":"明安世鳳撰","summary":"明安世鳳撰。世鳳有《燕居功課》，已著錄。此書以所見古器古刻古書畫各為跋語，凡六百九十五則，多涉議論，頗乏考據之功。","edition":"兩淮馬裕家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3022164","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-qingchaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NGJ8921271210348","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"清抄本","version":"v2","total_page":835,"paragraph_count":2355,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-chaoben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02056977","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"鈔本","version":"v2","total_page":705,"paragraph_count":6921,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hcUxCX":{"id":"GYL56hcUxCX","type":"work","title":"遊具雅編","authors":[{"name":"屠隆","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《遊具雅編》•一卷","author_info":"明屠隆撰","summary":"明屠隆撰。所載笠杖漁竿之屬，皆便於遊覽之具，故以為名。卷末附圖四式，一曰太極樽，一曰葫蘆樽，一曰山遊提盒，一曰提爐。雖書中所已具，以其形制皆須圖乃明，故複附繪於末。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=912399","type":"text"}]},"GYL56hs2huH":{"id":"GYL56hs2huH","type":"work","title":"華夷花木鳥獸珍玩考","authors":[{"name":"慎懋官","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《華夷花木鳥獸珍玩考》•十卷","author_info":"明慎懋官撰","summary":"明慎懋官撰。懋官字汝學，湖州人。是書凡花木考六卷，鳥獸考一卷，珍玩考一卷，續考二卷。或剽取舊說，或參以己語，或標出典，或不標出典，真偽雜糅，餖飣無緒。如楓樹一條稱謨按云云，似著此書者名謨。又木蓮樹一條稱元和十四年夏命道士毌邱元志寫，因題絕句云云，似著此書者在唐代。至衛懿公好鶴一條不引《左傳》而引傳奇俚詞，尤為不考。卷首自序一篇，詞極誇大，過矣。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":10},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=221510","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlishiqikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/SDZJ0747","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"万历时期刻本","version":"v5","total_page":993,"paragraph_count":1144,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlijiukeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY7247","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆九年(1581)刻本","version":"v7","total_page":1008,"paragraph_count":6267,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlijiukeben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02097197","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆九年刻本","version":"v4","total_page":983,"paragraph_count":9583,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL56hVFmCb":{"id":"GYL56hVFmCb","type":"work","title":"蕉窗九錄","authors":[{"name":"項元汴","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蕉窗九錄》•","author_info":"舊本題明項元汴撰","summary":"舊本題明項元汴撰。元汴字子京，秀水人。家藏書畫之富，甲於天下。今賞鑒家所稱項墨林者是也。是書首紙錄，次墨錄，次筆錄，次研錄，次帖錄，次書錄，次琴錄，次香錄。前有文彭序，稱大半采自吳文定《鑒古彙編》，間有刪潤。今考其書，陋略殊甚，彭序亦弇鄙不文。二人皆萬萬不至此，殆稍知字義之書賈，以二人有博雅名，依託之以炫俗也。","edition":"無卷數，江蘇巡撫采進本"}],"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=871602","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4528764","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-daoguangshiyichaoshi","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02097194","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"道光十一年晁氏活字印學海類編本","version":"v3","total_page":148,"paragraph_count":122,"check_type":"粗校"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true}}